    "</head>\n",
    "<body>\n",
    "  <h1>Pandas Profiling Bug</h1>\n",
    "  <p>An error occurred when using the <code>pandas_profiling</code> library with a real dataset. The error message indicates an issue related to numpy.</p>\n",
    "  <h2>Code Snippet:</h2>\n",
